---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import ParallaxSection from '../components/ParallaxSection.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../components/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<Base title="文化">
  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/culture-1.jpg"
    headingZh="舌尖上的乡愁"
    headingEn="Taste of Home"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">温州糯米饭、鱼丸汤、灯盏糕、炒粉干——这些地道的温州味道，是全球温州人心中最温暖的记忆。无论巴黎还是纽约，一碗糯米饭就是故乡。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">Sticky rice, fish ball soup, lantern cakes, stir-fried rice noodles — wherever Wenzhou people go, these flavors define home.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/culture-2.jpg"
    headingZh="温州方言"
    headingEn="The Wenzhou Dialect"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>温州话被誉为"中国最难懂的方言"之一，保留了大量古汉语的音韵特征。在海外温州人社区中，温州话依然是家庭和商会中的主要交流语言。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">Known as one of China's most difficult dialects, Wenzhouhua preserves ancient phonological features. It remains the primary language in diaspora homes and business associations.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/culture-3.jpg"
    headingZh="信仰与传统"
    headingEn="Faith and Tradition"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">妈祖信仰随着温州人的脚步走向世界。每年农历三月二十三妈祖诞辰，世界各地的温州社区都会举行隆重的祭祀活动，维系着文化与精神的纽带。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">Mazu worship travels with Wenzhou people worldwide. Each year on Mazu's birthday, communities gather in ceremony, preserving cultural and spiritual bonds.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>
</Base>

<script src="../scripts/parallax.js"></script>
<script src="../scripts/scroll-reveal.js"></script>
